{"type":"message","id":"76c30d3e","parentId":"70b88081","timestamp":"2026-04-01T07:11:28.171Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ez3irgw5gx4p_1","toolName":"sessions_list","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"count\": 2,\n  \"sessions\": [\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775027478193,\n      \"sessionId\": \"2f967b7d-c9e6-4da2-86e7-da277a87daa3\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 49161,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/2f967b7d-c9e6-4da2-86e7-da277a87daa3.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me check if there are active sessions first.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_ez3irgw5gx4p_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"activeMinutes\": 5,\n                \"messageLimit\": 1\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775027483590\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:1df084b4-9ecd-4003-8fd7-4d733dfada5f\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"displayName\": \"feishu:g-agent-main-subagent-1df084b4-9ecd-4003-8fd7-4d733dfada5f\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1775027307657,\n      \"sessionId\": \"b119a19c-99fb-4816-aae3-7fbabb9b60df\",\n      \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 44453,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"feishu\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/b119a19c-99fb-4816-aae3-7fbabb9b60df.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"I have good search results. Now let me compile the findings into a structured Markdown report.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"<final>\\n\\n## 2026年3-4月 企业数字化、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务行业动态\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 一、企业数字化转型\\n\\n**政策加码，数据与AI双轮驱动**\\n\\n2026年3月，国家与地方协同推进企业数字化转型，工信部启动\\\"工业数据筑基行动\\\"，目标到2026年底建成重点行业数据可信互联平台，培育行业大模型与工业智能体落地应用。四部门联合发布《中小企业数字化赋能专项行动方案(2025—2027年)》，明确到2027年规上工业中小企业关键工序数控化率达75%、上云率超40%。北京市出台政策最高补贴500万元支持企业转型，上海市推行\\\"免申即享\\\"简化申请流程。核心趋势：数据作为核心生产要素，AI在工业领域规模化应用提速，中小企业与产业链\\\"链式改造\\\"协同推进。\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 二、智能安防\\n\\n**AI从\\\"事后追溯\\\"向\\\"事中预警\\\"全面升级**\\n\\n智能安防行业加速向主动预警演进。海康威视在陕西彬长矿业部署的\\\"AI智能识别多级联动\\\"系统已实现周界攀爬告警、人员倒伏及温度异常自动弹窗报警。云端集成防盗报警系统通过物联网技术实现毫秒级异常侦测，联动摄像头、灯光等设备形成防御闭环。11月北京安博会以\\\"数智世界 全域安全\\\"为主题，AI大模型、智能芯片驱动的主动预警与全域数据可视化成为核心展示方向。\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 三、网络系统集成\\n\\n**多系统融合与统一平台成为主流建设模式**\\n\\n网络系统集成领域呈现IT/OT/物理安全三大系统融合趋势。41%的行业决策者将安全系统统一平台列为优先事项，要求物理安全与IT系统在互操作性、数据治理及网络安全上标准统一。华为发布智慧变电站解决方案，整合机器视觉、光纤传感、边缘计算，实现周界防护、智能巡检与视频监控一体化，替代传统人工巡视。以统一平台为核心的融合方案简化施工流程、降低运维成本，成为行业主流建设路径。\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 四、IT运维服务\\n\\n**智能化、国产化、全生命周期管理成为升级方向**\\n\\nIT运维服务向智能化全面转型。浪潮信息InManage V7平台融合物联网、AI、数字孪生技术，实现数据中心IT资产全生命周期管理，支持RFID动态盘点。针对国产化合规需求，支持国产操作系统的视频监控网络运维方案已可监控国产CPU、服务器及数据库，满足特殊行业合规要求。开源AI智能体安全风险受关注，\\\"AI效能+数据安全\\\"一体化方案成为新兴探索方向。\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 五、综合趋势\\n\\n| 方向 | 核心要点 |\\n|------|----------|\\n| **数智化** | AI大模型、工业智能体从试点走向规模化落地 |\\n| **自主化** | 国产芯片、国产操作系统成合规刚需 |\\n| **融合化** | IT/OT/物理安全三域协同，统一平台替代孤岛系统 |\\n| **场景化** | 从通用方案转向垂直行业定制（如智慧变电站、智慧矿山） |\\n| **服务化** | 运维从被动响应转向全生命周期主动管理 |\\n\\n---\\n\\n*信息来源：综合工信部政策文件、行业展会动态及头部企业（海康威视、华为、浪潮信息）公开信息，搜索时间2026年3-4月。*\\n\\n</final>\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"minimax\",\n          \"model\": \"MiniMax-M2.7\",\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1775027282357\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":2,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1775027478193,"sessionId":"2f967b7d-c9e6-4da2-86e7-da277a87daa3","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":49161,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/2f967b7d-c9e6-4da2-86e7-da277a87daa3.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check if there are active sessions first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ez3irgw5gx4p_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775027483590}]},{"key":"agent:main:subagent:1df084b4-9ecd-4003-8fd7-4d733dfada5f","kind":"other","channel":"feishu","displayName":"feishu:g-agent-main-subagent-1df084b4-9ecd-4003-8fd7-4d733dfada5f","deliveryContext":{"channel":"feishu"},"updatedAt":1775027307657,"sessionId":"b119a19c-99fb-4816-aae3-7fbabb9b60df","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44453,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"feishu","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/b119a19c-99fb-4816-aae3-7fbabb9b60df.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I have good search results. Now let me compile the findings into a structured Markdown report."},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n\n## 2026年3-4月 企业数字化、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务行业动态\n\n---\n\n### 一、企业数字化转型\n\n**政策加码，数据与AI双轮驱动**\n\n2026年3月，国家与地方协同推进企业数字化转型，工信部启动\"工业数据筑基行动\"，目标到2026年底建成重点行业数据可信互联平台，培育行业大模型与工业智能体落地应用。四部门联合发布《中小企业数字化赋能专项行动方案(2025—2027年)》，明确到2027年规上工业中小企业关键工序数控化率达75%、上云率超40%。北京市出台政策最高补贴500万元支持企业转型，上海市推行\"免申即享\"简化申请流程。核心趋势：数据作为核心生产要素，AI在工业领域规模化应用提速，中小企业与产业链\"链式改造\"协同推进。\n\n---\n\n### 二、智能安防\n\n**AI从\"事后追溯\"向\"事中预警\"全面升级**\n\n智能安防行业加速向主动预警演进。海康威视在陕西彬长矿业部署的\"AI智能识别多级联动\"系统已实现周界攀爬告警、人员倒伏及温度异常自动弹窗报警。云端集成防盗报警系统通过物联网技术实现毫秒级异常侦测，联动摄像头、灯光等设备形成防御闭环。11月北京安博会以\"数智世界 全域安全\"为主题，AI大模型、智能芯片驱动的主动预警与全域数据可视化成为核心展示方向。\n\n---\n\n### 三、网络系统集成\n\n**多系统融合与统一平台成为主流建设模式**\n\n网络系统集成领域呈现IT/OT/物理安全三大系统融合趋势。41%的行业决策者将安全系统统一平台列为优先事项，要求物理安全与IT系统在互操作性、数据治理及网络安全上标准统一。华为发布智慧变电站解决方案，整合机器视觉、光纤传感、边缘计算，实现周界防护、智能巡检与视频监控一体化，替代传统人工巡视。以统一平台为核心的融合方案简化施工流程、降低运维成本，成为行业主流建设路径。\n\n---\n\n### 四、IT运维服务\n\n**智能化、国产化、全生命周期管理成为升级方向**\n\nIT运维服务向智能化全面转型。浪潮信息InManage V7平台融合物联网、AI、数字孪生技术，实现数据中心IT资产全生命周期管理，支持RFID动态盘点。针对国产化合规需求，支持国产操作系统的视频监控网络运维方案已可监控国产CPU、服务器及数据库，满足特殊行业合规要求。开源AI智能体安全风险受关注，\"AI效能+数据安全\"一体化方案成为新兴探索方向。\n\n---\n\n### 五、综合趋势\n\n| 方向 | 核心要点 |\n|------|----------|\n| **数智化** | AI大模型、工业智能体从试点走向规模化落地 |\n| **自主化** | 国产芯片、国产操作系统成合规刚需 |\n| **融合化** | IT/OT/物理安全三域协同，统一平台替代孤岛系统 |\n| **场景化** | 从通用方案转向垂直行业定制（如智慧变电站、智慧矿山） |\n| **服务化** | 运维从被动响应转向全生命周期主动管理 |\n\n---\n\n*信息来源：综合工信部政策文件、行业展会动态及头部企业（海康威视、华为、浪潮信息）公开信息，搜索时间2026年3-4月。*\n\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775027282357}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775027488127}}
{"type":"message","id":"010caf8d","parentId":"76c30d3e","timestamp":"2026-04-01T07:11:42.973Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There are 2 sessions. The first one is this cron job itself (updated just now), and the second one is a feishu subagent session that was last updated at 1775027307657, which is about 1775027478193 - 1775027307657 = 170536ms ≈ 170 seconds ≈ 2.8 minutes ago. So there IS recent activity on the feishu session (within the last 5 minutes).\n\nActually, wait - let me recalculate. Current time is 1775027483590 (from the cron session's last message). The feishu session was last updated at 1775027307657. The difference is 1775027483590 - 1775027307657 = 175933ms ≈ 2.9 minutes ago. \n\nThe feishu session updated 2.9 minutes ago falls within the 5-minute threshold, so that's definitely active. But I need to think about what \"活跃对话\" actually means here—it's asking for user messages specifically, not just any session activity. The feishu session shows an assistant message, not a user message, so I should verify whether that's what counts as \"active dialogue\" in this context.\n\nLooking at the timestamp difference between when the cron job fired and the feishu session's last update, it's about 2.9 minutes, which is within the 5-minute window. But the session only shows an assistant message, not a user message, so this might not qualify as an active user conversation. The cron task itself is still running and waiting for me to complete it. Since this is the cron session and the feishu session has activity within the last few minutes, I should treat this as having an active conversation happening. I'll save the search results that were already compiled and continue from there.","thinkingSignature":"0c054a15f13800831aa62bb4574c923f220b87904d2684dc30790de0a014ee0a"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到活跃对话（feishu 子Agent session 于约3分钟前有活动），不执行自主学习。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage"